overview: Foreign, Punjabi Language, India, Foreign Languages, Foreign Regions - A young man and woman meet when they each are registered with a marriage bureau by parents hoping to wed them to people abroad. But tempers fly when it's discovered that the agency is a scam. In the ensuing chaos, the young couple discovers a mutual attraction that eventually leads to love and marriage. Sukhjinder Shera directs this romantic comedy.
title: Sidha Chall Canada Nu
